Rename DENYLIST-latest to DENYLIST-LATEST

From: Shung-Hsi Yu <shung-hsi.yu@suse.com>

Capitalization matters, and since we're using 'LATEST' instead of
'latest' as the kernel variable (below), we should have the deny list
files named accordingly.

  vmtest-mainline:
    strategy:
      fail-fast: false
      matrix:
        include:
          - kernel: 'LATEST'
            runs_on: 'ubuntu-24.04'
            arch: 'x86_64'
            llvm-version: '22'
            pahole: 'master'
    name: Mainline Linux ${{ matrix.kernel }} llvm-${{ matrix.llvm-version }}
    uses: ./.github/workflows/vmtest-mainline.yml

Signed-off-by: Shung-Hsi Yu <shung-hsi.yu@suse.com>
